flowchart LR
    H[Hypothesis and mechanism] --> R[Pre-register experiment]
    R --> P[Define eligible population]
    P --> A[Randomize or assign treatment]
    A --> E[Record actual exposure]
    E --> M[Measure primary outcomes and guardrails]
    M --> C[Estimate causal effect]
    C --> D{Decision}
    D -->|Adopt| O[Operational rollout]
    D -->|Revise| H
    D -->|Reject| K[Record learning]

    X[External factors and concurrent changes] -. annotate .-> M
    Q[Data quality and metric versions] -. govern .-> M
    O --> K
